Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.10,0:01:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不喜欢念咒语吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.69,0:02:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.99,0:02:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.17,0:02:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.14,0:02:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在工作？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.44,0:02:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在午休
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.11,0:02:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.16,0:02:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.44,0:02:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天回来晚了不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.95,0:02:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,饭…很好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.17,0:02:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这些？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.52,0:02:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就只有这些吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.20,0:02:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.75,0:02:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你打电话打扰到你了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.10,0:02:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.19,0:02:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天一起去喝点什么吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.31,0:02:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 今天有些应酬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.91,0:02:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.29,0:02:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别喝太多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.31,0:02:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你酒量不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.27,0:03:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那挂断吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.79,0:03:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然打电话过来  不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.91,0:03:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.34,0:03:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.00,0:03:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.30,0:03:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见 努力工作哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.18,0:03:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对遥是责任感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.34,0:03:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的女朋友是水月你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.41,0:03:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前辈  他在准备幽会吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.63,0:03:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,错不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.16,0:03:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这种正忙得不可开交的午饭时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.49,0:03:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那里贼兮兮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.56,0:03:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样只有让他尝尝「天诛」了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.01,0:03:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦  天诛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.64,0:03:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脱光他衣服拖着去游街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.35,0:03:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让他在这个街区再也呆不下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.13,0:03:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦？这个很有趣呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.60,0:03:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,店长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.69,0:03:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么拖谁去游街？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.32,0:03:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.24,0:03:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.28,0:04:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有工作呢  快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.67,0:04:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.04,0:04:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.55,0:04:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是说拖出去游街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.53,0:04:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.83,0:04:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很长的电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.60,0:04:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.63,0:04:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.02,0:04:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呀 真没用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.06,0:04:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克制自己的七情六欲…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.45,0:04:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在学生时代固然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.12,0:04:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,步入社会却只有弊大于利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.71,0:04:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要把事情想得太复杂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.07,0:04:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否则  进展顺利的事也会受阻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.82,0:04:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.53,0:04:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看起来就这么不幸吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.05,0:04:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这么惨吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.96,0:04:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.25,0:04:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说了奇怪的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.23,0:04:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于看到你像个正常人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.55,0:04:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚痛快地玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.07,0:05:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.36,0:05:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.69,0:05:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天很晚啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.14,0:05:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,探视时间已经过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.45,0:05:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打工时间延长了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.83,0:05:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.03,0:05:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.25,0:05:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.73,0:05:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  男朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.11,0:05:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天你对凉宫做过什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.20,0:05:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 文绪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.15,0:05:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  天川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.31,0:05:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是不是作了什么约定？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.47,0:05:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约定？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.04,0:05:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这件事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.94,0:05:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也算不上约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.45,0:05:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是一起念了咒语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.48,0:05:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那有什么关系吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.67,0:05:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咒语？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.93,0:05:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"唧唧呜呜啪"这样的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.07,0:05:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  有些不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.66,0:05:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过差不多啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.14,0:05:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥告诉你的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.78,0:05:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有详细地说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.15,0:05:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过提起的时候看上去很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.69,0:05:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她记得啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.35,0:06:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.43,0:06:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近凉宫的认知力めきめき恢复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.43,0:06:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0250,,{\fs10}注：めきめき有两个意思，一个是快\N另一个是骨头或树木折断的声音\N这里文绪误解成后者了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.99,0:06:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.29,0:06:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用“めきめき”不觉得奇怪吗？ 天川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.29,0:06:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.59,0:06:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那めりめり
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.59,0:06:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0270,,{\fs10}注：めりめり表示树木或骨头慢慢被拗断时发出的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.08,0:06:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.68,0:06:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那むきむき？（むきむき：各种方面）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.17,0:06:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,もりもり？（もりもり：狼吞虎咽的样子）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.04,0:06:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,もりもり？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.70,0:06:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.19,0:06:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是好势头吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.05,0:06:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对遥来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.40,0:06:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.42,0:06:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也多亏了男朋友呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.95,0:06:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 鸣海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.20,0:06:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,医生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.64,0:06:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天很晚呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.16,0:06:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在能去看她吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.70,0:06:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.15,0:06:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在等你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.85,0:06:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.19,0:06:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天来晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.11,0:06:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.31,0:07:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还是来了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.01,0:07:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.38,0:07:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.55,0:07:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.46,0:07:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我脸上有什么吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.44,0:07:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.42,0:07:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚熬夜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.74,0:07:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天有点发呆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.59,0:07:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,熬夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.63,0:07:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 对身体可不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.49,0:07:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觉得学习有点意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.92,0:07:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样也不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.20,0:07:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正离考试还有段时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.42,0:07:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 会注意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.70,0:07:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保证
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.98,0:07:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 保证
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.05,0:07:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.81,0:07:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.73,0:07:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觉得无聊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.99,0:07:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.11,0:07:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你脸上写着无聊哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.35,0:08:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.29,0:08:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的"对不起"也差不多听腻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.62,0:08:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  献丑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.06,0:08:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.26,0:08:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速濑的演唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.02,0:08:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上司的命令  上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.14,0:08:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我唱歌不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.76,0:08:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.72,0:08:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我也一起唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.89,0:08:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样行了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.55,0:08:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽情的唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.39,0:08:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把心里的不痛快都发泄出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.33,0:08:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 那么谁来点歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.00,0:08:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.05,0:09:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 又要念咒语吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.36,0:09:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢你这么说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.23,0:09:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.64,0:09:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 念咒语吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.91,0:09:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.84,0:09:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是喝得太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.04,0:09:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 喝太多了  前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.33,0:09:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轻松点了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.99,0:09:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  多谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.56,0:09:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.14,0:09:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能走吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.53,0:09:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.76,0:09:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.02,0:09:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.61,0:10:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.00,0:10:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使两人无法牵手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.64,0:10:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我们依然牢记…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.46,0:10:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.35,0:10:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.60,0:10:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我包忘了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.07,0:10:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.28,0:10:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜 这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.14,0:10:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.67,0:11:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜  等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.50,0:11:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.33,0:11:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好过分的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.48,0:11:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明不是真心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.63,0:11:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对 那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.26,0:11:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.43,0:11:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫不对？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.23,0:11:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西怎么不对了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.31,0:11:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣海喜欢的不是姐姐吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.78,0:11:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽说姐姐想见你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.70,0:11:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那是 那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.48,0:11:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你不要再玩弄姐姐的感情了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.77,0:11:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对…不是这样的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.35,0:12:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…其实我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.47,0:12:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你来了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.00,0:12:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水月？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.06,0:12:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 孝之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.60,0:12:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 喝醉了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.79,0:12:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没醉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.68,0:12:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.98,0:12:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在研究呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.10,0:12:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近太忙 你是不是忘了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.75,0:12:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遥好像也在渐渐好转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.75,0:12:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得也该决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.52,0:12:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到一套好的房子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.16,0:12:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…虽然有点贵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.37,0:12:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两个人合伙的话应该能买下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.24,0:12:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,离车站也很近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.92,0:13:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和这里一样是最边上的房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.34,0:13:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个周末一起去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.35,0:13:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先给房产商打个电话吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.80,0:13:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要到周末才决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.85,0:13:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天就打电话确认～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.43,0:13:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果周末去 周六还是周日？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.72,0:13:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.48,0:13:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我休息 哪天都没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.03,0:13:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.10,0:13:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽量快点比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.08,0:13:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那周六吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.57,0:13:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是周日？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.09,0:13:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.90,0:13:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搬家…还不需要这么急吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.53,0:13:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等到遥的事告一段落也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.99,0:13:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说 说什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.37,0:13:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说要搬家的不是孝之吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.66,0:13:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是孝之说一起住吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.40,0:13:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以等遥她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.40,0:13:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有关系吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.45,0:13:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这和遥的事告一段落什么的\N根本没关系吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.11,0:14:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我们之间的问题吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.69,0:14:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发什么脾气呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.61,0:14:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我发脾气 当然要发脾气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.19,0:14:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你冷静点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.92,0:14:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有说不搬吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.17,0:14:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候跟她说？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.97,0:14:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和孝之的事情什么时候和遥说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.85,0:14:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实根本就不想说吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.22,0:14:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.39,0:14:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不出口吧 是吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.34,0:14:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你适可而止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.92,0:14:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明酒量不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.55,0:14:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还喝成这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.90,0:14:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.38,0:14:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.49,0:14:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很危险的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.08,0:14:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.90,0:14:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  我为什么不能喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.83,0:14:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醉了又怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.70,0:14:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我好难过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.40,0:15:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我好痛苦啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.27,0:15:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.97,0:15:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遇到什么事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.59,0:15:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明还喜欢她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.59,0:15:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之还是喜欢遥吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.06,0:15:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.44,0:15:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.54,0:15:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.43,0:15:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说傻话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.79,0:15:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说过的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.75,0:15:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没这种事 没关系的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.64,0:15:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是真心话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.06,0:15:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.34,0:15:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.36,0:15:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不是什么真心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.90,0:15:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之根本就不爱我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.84,0:15:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水月 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.95,0:15:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.09,0:16:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.72,0:16:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孝之前辈 不怎么精神呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.74,0:16:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是幽会失败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.84,0:16:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后对自己的无能感到丧气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.10,0:16:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那还真是痛苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.72,0:16:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是没腔调  大笨牛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.26,0:16:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣海 正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.22,0:16:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.22,0:16:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,介绍一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.76,0:16:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SKY TEMPLE本部人事部伊藤先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.15,0:16:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面 我是伊藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.27,0:16:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.16,0:16:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正好说到你的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.57,0:16:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣海 你说过你不是学生吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.62,0:17:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当中有什么原委吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.59,0:17:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.40,0:17:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.93,0:17:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞人事的坏习惯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.55,0:17:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面就这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.59,0:17:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我还有事情忙 改天再来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.67,0:17:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请多多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.10,0:17:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鸣海 再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.70,0:17:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他总是很忙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.43,0:17:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人事部的人来干什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.69,0:17:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不明白吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.27,0:17:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这间店里有一个人满脑子只有幽会\N这一事实终于传到本部了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.76,0:17:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放任不管的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.11,0:17:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会影响到店的形象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.10,0:17:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以实地调查来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.82,0:17:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可不得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.84,0:17:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不炒这家伙魷鱼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.67,0:17:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这间店就没有未来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.43,0:17:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道这间店要关门？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.30,0:17:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这还真是大件事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.71,0:18:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您也真是的  店长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.17,0:18:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可能嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.66,0:18:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么？  丧家犬...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.10,0:18:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要说影响形象的问题人物应该是这人吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.37,0:18:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.74,0:18:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.97,0:18:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.29,0:18:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又一个冲击性的事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.94,0:18:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连真由都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.21,0:18:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对着客人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.40,0:18:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你点菜要点到什么时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.07,0:18:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.29,0:18:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动作快点  这个畜牲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.92,0:18:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的台词哪里有形象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.79,0:18:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.88,0:18:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么时候做过这样的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.16,0:18:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说过吧 玉野
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.00,0:18:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一周大概要说三次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.76,0:18:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听到了吧 店长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.45,0:18:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个可头痛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.80,0:18:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坏掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.85,0:18:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.20,0:18:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我不杀了你这畜生！
